text: Dane Jeffrey Cook (born March 18, 1972 in Cambridge, Massachusetts) is an American comedian and actor. Cook has performed in many major arenas like the Madison Square Garden. ==Discography== Dane Cook has released 5 comedy albums: *Harmful If Swallowed (2003) *Retaliation (2005) *Rough Around the Edges: Live from Madison Square Garden (2007) *Isolated Incident (2008) *I Did My Best: Greatest Hits Album (2010) ==Other websites== *Dane Cook's Official website * Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Cambridge, Massachusetts Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:American television writers Category:Comedians from Massachusetts
